    "name": "ETH RWA market - remove Saturn assets from AlphaGrowth mAPOLLO",
    "description": "Removes Saturn sUSDat and USDat from the AlphaGrowth mAPOLLO/RWA market. Sets true zero supply/borrow caps on the Saturn EVaults using AmountCap raw value 1, and immediately zeros all active LTV relationships that allow Saturn assets to be borrowed or used as collateral. Does not clear EulerRouter pricing/resolved-vault routes so existing positions can still be priced for repayment, withdrawal, or liquidation unwind."
